{"tid":496769,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【好打得】支国保母喺𨋢內打少主 一分鐘12連擊","createTime":"2017-12-12T04:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T06:11:48.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ac6de4b82e0feccc345cdc24666247af67368eaa","tid":496769,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T04:48:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bXaGIRjgPq0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbXaGIRjgPq0&d=Yt7A02elDoz4Cy37BAznh%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=796f06aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bXaGIRjgPq0</a><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】河南鄭州一名保母周二（5日）在升降機內毆打孩子的閉路電視影片在網上熱傳，警方已拘捕保母。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，事發小區為鄭州恆大名都小區。閉路電視影片顯示，一名身穿粉紅色衣服的女子將孩子交到保母手上，升降機關門後，由於孩子哭鬧，保母先舉起右手作勢嚇嚇孩子，隨後捶打孩子的腹部6次。之後保母將孩子放進嬰兒車後，繼續捶打孩子的頭部2次、背部4次，並多次搖晃孩子的身體及嬰兒車，直至走出升降機，整個虐打過程為一分鐘。警方目前已介入調查事件，保母已被捕。"},{"pid":"e155e92c7d8446c48e9030123e29dcfe75698f60","tid":496769,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T04:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好佩服強國經常有閉路電視影片流出"},{"pid":"7560187705123d0113af2f8739641152285286b5","tid":496769,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T05:02:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba16e4a0c02dd6fd068e46b6ea396e63c8af077d","tid":496769,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T05:10:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好佩服強國經常有閉路電視影片流出</blockquote><br />\n香港大把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14589f54cbbea0bb4fb0fe6e8fc6c2d102153ce","tid":496769,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T05:14:00.000Z","msg":"如果你受罰，就因為你犯罪了<br />\n個細路身有屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e591c6c3e55d94179ad85a0696ef3be1826649","tid":496769,"uid":8949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit